    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I can't reproduce this. `priv_getPrivateTransaction` doesn't have blockNumber or transactionIndex. `priv_getTransactionReceipt` and `eth_getTransaction` both do, and they are in hex. \n\n`priv_getPrivateTransaction` has gas, gasPrice, nonce, and value all using Quantity.create() to get hex. See https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/256e5c914d8f6559cf52f2fa93494502986806c5/ethereum/api/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/ethereum/api/jsonrpc/internal/results/privacy/PrivateTransactionResult.java#L40",
